videos.description: Manny Wilkins run for 3 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Manny Wilkins hurdles his way to the end zone for opening score

videos.description: Kalen Ballage run for 52 yds for a TD
videos.headline: 52-yard run by Ballage puts Arizon state up 11

videos.description: Robert Taylor adds one of the highlight reel starting deep in his own end zone and going the length of the field, with a nifty spin move thrown in, to go 100 yards for a kickoff return touchdown for Washington State.
videos.headline: Spin move and super speed gets Wazzu a 100-yard kickoff return TD

videos.description: Luke Falk pass complete to Tavares Martin Jr. for 9 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Wazzu takes the lead on Tavares Martin Jr 9-yard catch

videos.description: Gerard Wicks run for 3 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Gerard Wicks 3-Yard Run puts Wazzu up 10

videos.description: Luke Falk pass complete to Jamal Morrow for 3 yds for a TD (Erik Powell KICK)
videos.headline: Jamal Morrow 3-yard TD catch puts Wazzu up 17

videos.description: Demario Richard run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: Demario Richard brings Arizona St within 10

videos.description: Luke Falk pass complete to Gabe Marks for 52 yds for a TD
videos.headline: L. Falk pass,to G. Marks for 52 yds for a TD

videos.description: Tim White takes the punt off the bounce and then dances around the Washington State coverage team, gets a few needed blocks and then is gone for 70 yards to the house. Arizona State adds a two-point conversion to cut the lead to 37-29.
videos.headline: White shows off all kinds of moves for 70-yard punt return TD
